<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Yahweh God of hosts,</para>

<para style="q1">how long will you be angry at your people when they pray?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />You have fed them with the bread of tears</para>

<para style="q1">and given them tears to drink in great quantities.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />You make us something for our neighbors to argue over,</para>

<para style="q1">and our enemies laugh about us among themselves.</para>
